---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs Capterra — Collect Testimonials vs Listing on Review Sites | SocialProof" description="Capterra is a B2B software directory — not a testimonial tool. SocialProof lets you collect testimonials directly from clients and embed them on your website. Free to start." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/vs/capterra">
<style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .vs-badge { display: inline-block; background: #f0f0f0; color: #555; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: .35rem .75rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #4f46e5; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #444; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .compare-table th { padding: .75rem 1rem; text-align: left; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; color: #888; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; }
    .compare-table th:nth-child(2) { color: #4f46e5; }
    .compare-table td { padding: .85rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 0.97rem; vertical-align: top; }
    .compare-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .compare-table td:first-child { color: #555; font-weight: 500; }
    .yes { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
    .no { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; }
    .partial { color: #d97706; font-weight: 600; }
    .note-box { background: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #bae6fd; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .bottom-cta { text-align: center; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 3.5rem 2rem; margin: 3rem 0; }
    .bottom-cta h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    .bottom-cta p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.8); margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .bottom-cta a { display: inline-block; background: #fff; color: #4f46e5; padding: .9rem 2.25rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
</style>
<main>
  <div class="hero">
    <span class="vs-badge">Comparison</span>
    <h1>SocialProof vs <span>Capterra</span></h1>
    <p>Capterra is a software directory for B2B buyers researching tools. SocialProof is a testimonial collection and display tool for service businesses. They solve fundamentally different problems — here's what each is actually for.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="hero-cta">Try SocialProof Free →</a>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="note-box">
      <strong>Not a direct comparison:</strong> Capterra and SocialProof aren't really competitors — Capterra is a B2B discovery platform, while SocialProof is a tool to collect and display testimonials on your own website. You might use both for different purposes.
    </div>

    <h2>What each tool actually does</h2>
    <table class="compare-table">
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Job to be done</th><th>SocialProof</th><th>Capterra</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Collect testimonials from clients</td><td class="yes">✓ Yes — core feature</td><td class="no">Not the purpose</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Display testimonials on YOUR site</td><td class="yes">✓ Yes — embeddable widget</td><td class="no">Reviews live on Capterra</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Help new buyers discover your software</td><td class="no">Not the purpose</td><td class="yes">✓ Yes — core feature</td></tr>
        <tr><td>B2B software listings</td><td class="no">Not applicable</td><td class="yes">✓ Yes</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Approve reviews before display</td><td class="yes">✓ Yes</td><td class="no">Capterra controls review display</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Works for service businesses</td><td class="yes">✓ Yes — any industry</td><td class="no">Software companies only</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Embed on your site</td><td class="yes">✓ Copy/paste widget</td><td class="partial">Badge links to Capterra</td></tr>
        <tr><td>You own the testimonials</td><td class="yes">✓ Yes — export anytime</td><td class="no">Capterra owns the data</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Starting cost</td><td class="yes">Free</td><td class="partial">Free listing (paid promotion available)</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>When Capterra is the right choice</h2>
    <p>If you're a B2B software company looking to be discovered by buyers who are actively comparing tools, Capterra is a powerful discovery channel. Buyers search Capterra for "project management software" or "accounting tools" and compare options.</p>

    <h2>When SocialProof is the right choice</h2>
    <p>If you want to collect testimonials from your existing clients and display them on your website to convert new visitors, SocialProof is the right tool. This works for any business — freelancers, agencies, consultants, service businesses, coaches, and yes, software companies too.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:1rem;">SocialProof testimonials live on <em>your</em> site, in <em>your</em> design, serving <em>your</em> conversion goals. Not on a third-party platform where your competitors can advertise next to your listing.</p>

    <h2>Use both together</h2>
    <p>Many SaaS companies list on Capterra for discovery AND use SocialProof (or a similar tool) to display their best testimonials on their own website. The review collections are complementary: Capterra for top-of-funnel discovery, on-site testimonials for conversion.</p>

    <div class="bottom-cta">
      <h2>Collect testimonials you actually own</h2>
      <p>Display client testimonials on your website — where you control the experience. Free forever for 1 widget.</p>
      <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup">Start Free — No Credit Card →</a>
    </div>

    <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#888;margin-top:2rem;">Also compare: <a href="/vs/google-reviews">vs Google Reviews</a> · <a href="/vs/yelp">vs Yelp</a> · <a href="/vs/trustpilot">vs Trustpilot</a> · <a href="/vs/testimonial-io">vs Testimonial.io</a> · <a href="/vs/senja">vs Senja</a></p>
  </section>
</main>
</Base>
